														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2469493">
									

<p>Emma and Roger primarily, but by including Emma, you are including everything in the <em>On Mount Golgotha Canon</em> as well. This is the only contest series that I have read so far (I am still not quite done reading every one) that feels connected like this one does. Your team is the only one that used the opportunity to really build on existing narratives, and the only one that really built your contest entries around planned future work as well.</p>
<p>As far as <a href="/scp-2337">SCP-2337</a> goes, he is logically in Eta-11s wheelhouse, since his sonic effects are really the most immediately hazardous thing about him.</p>

							</div>

								
