			<div class="content" id="post-content-2471150">
									

<p>Solid piece of writing. This sets up a clear story, introduces to us to the main players in a manner that isn't just a straight info-dump, and gives us a little characterization to chew on as readers. I'm not an overarching canon person, but I like how carefully constructed this was in relation to other works; the cross-references all make sense, and represent a diversity of material from the wiki.</p>
<p>Nice work.</p>

